name: Ashley Bradford
note: I already knew about Nike Air Force Shoes. It stays behind the big players in the world. I feel very comfortable after wear this. It doesn’t make you feel tired while walking later. The funniest thing is that even if you walk after it you will feel like you are running but believe me you will never feel like you are tired. In a word, there is magic in these shoes. Thank you Nike for giving us such an offer.

name: Morgan Bruce
note: Nike Air Force is a great shoes in a word. It will be perfect for you. When you wear this you get a fitness partner. You will no longer be single, trust me. I was single before I bought these shoes. Now I have two girlfriends. One is my true girlfriend and the other is my true girlfriend. That is no one else it is my nikey air force shoes !! ha ha. I'm joking. Nike Air Force Shoes are really good shoes. Buy it.

name: Robles Mcconnell
note: I don't think I need to say anything new about Nike. An offer that we would like to thank Shoes Mania for receiving from Nike. My friend & I bought two pairs of Nike Air Force shoes for Eid from Shoes Mania. Haven't seen it yet. I'll wear it on Eid day. I can't stand the delay anymore, when Eid will come, and when I'll wear my favorite shoes. Please coming Eid, I badly miss you. I'll wear my shoes, comiiing.
